{"title":"农业跃进十五绝","authors":["萧向荣"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":1,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"农业跃进十五绝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萧向荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破除迷信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一唱雄鸡亿户开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朝暾明艳照尧台。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"破除迷信驱邪说，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"解放灵思立?瑰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦战三年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农耕一马竟当先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦战三年改旧笺。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋向地球挥搏斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力争高耸上峰巅。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大兴水利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干涝从来苦折磨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍天无眼众生何。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千军直捣顽龙府，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱魃潜踪水不波。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"积肥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬春忙碌积农肥，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沤铲烧挖灰粪泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亩产万斤嫌未足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心潮争逐翠涛飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深耕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良土壤倡深耕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻起新泥增沃层。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旱湿普挖一尺几，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀虫除草扎牢根。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"良种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"麦稻品种择优良，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"耐冻驱虫抗力强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分蘖整齐穗粒大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早成丰产出群芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"合理密植"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水肥土种各咸宜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"密植纵横破旧规。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日照通风俱满足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千斤稳插上游旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"防治病虫害"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"作物繁生靠护持，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青黄不许病虫滋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预防药杀多功效，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"粒粒丰盈压翠枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良农具"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万众深谋发巧思，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良农具出神奇。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"减劳增速寻常事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"誉满田园喜展眉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"加强田间管理"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"种后还需尽措施，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤劳经管不违时。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"知冷知热知饥饱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"气力堆成玉满枝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"除四害"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四除豪气古今无，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"远瞩高瞻臂一呼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼠雀蚊蝇俱可灭，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人间何事足踌躇？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扫盲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田头书本喜盈盈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"民校添灯夜读声。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男女壮青攻路虎，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"争夸双眼放光明。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新问题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小社人少势单孤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳物资金总缺如。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欲举雄心力不足，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共谋合议策良图。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民公社化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小社合并大和公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五亿潮后破浪风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开辟农村新面貌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葵花朝日水朝东。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大丰收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捷讯频传腊鼓喧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉粮双举庆加番。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"古今中外无前例，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行见来年更一掀。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}